{
  "texts": [
    "This session commenced with an informative video lasting approximately ten minutes, which demonstrated the project's objectives, hardware setup, virtual driving environment, route, and, notably, three of the five ADAS functions.",
    "The video's decision to focus on only three ADAS functions was informed by the need to simulate the experience of purchasing a new vehicle, where car dealers typically showcase a limited number of key functions due to time constraints and legal limitations (Murtaza et al., 2022b).",
    "Meticulous design underscored this methodology to ensure an accurate explanation of the experiment setup and a professional demonstration of the ADAS functions.",
    "To maintain consistency across the study and ensure that all participants receive the same level of information, video recordings were utilised as the medium for training and demonstration.",
    "This approach aligns with the findings of (Ebnali et al., 2019; Zahabi et al., 2020), who suggest video-based training as one of the highly effective methods."
  ]
}